## External Sharing (DMZ)

The **DMZ** cluster (`{{ .DMZStream.Cluster }}`) hosts the `{{ .DMZStream.Name }}` stream (wave 2 — provisioned last). It re-publishes a filtered subset of central traffic under public subjects for external consumers.

- Provision the DMZ cluster's slice after central and regional (wave 2); apply the Stream CRs in `{{ .DMZPath }}`.
- The public subjects and per-consumer share names are listed in [`dmz-catalog.md`](dmz-catalog.md).
- Issue per-consumer subscribe-only JWTs scoped to each share's public subject (sub-project B / PKI). Consumers receive a credential that cannot publish or access internal subjects.
